   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure you have a serial port on the local computer. Disable
any services that uses that port.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Connect the serial cable (Reality part number: 940-0299) to the
serial port on the computer and the serial configuration port on the
NMC.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Start a terminal emulator and configure the connected serial
port on to:<table class="- topic/table ">
                     <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                        <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                        <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                        <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Name</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Value</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Baud rate</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">9600 bps</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Data</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">8 bit</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Parity</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Stop</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p translate="no" class="- topic/p ">1 bit</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row class="- topic/row ">
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">Flow control</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                                 <p class="- topic/p ">None</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol> repeatedly
to get the user name prompt.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reset</uicontrol> button
on the front panel of the NMC to start the reboot sequence.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reset</uicontrol> button
again during the reboot just when the status LED starts to flash orange
and green. This will temporary reset the user name and password to
their default settings for 30 seconds, see table <xref href="NMC_User_Accounts_and_Access_CPT_0000332535.dita#UserAccountsAndAccess-5E2E507C/DefaultUserAndPasswordSettings-AAE2F9B2"
                        scope="local"
                        type="table"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enter</uicontrol> repeatedly
to get the user name prompt. Use the default user name and password <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">apc</codeph> to login.</p>
               <note class="- topic/note ">When the prompt is
displayed you need to login within 30 seconds, else the password needs
to be reset again.</note>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">To set a new password type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">user —n
&lt;current user name&gt; —pw &lt;new user password&gt;</codeph>.
For example, to change the password to abcXYZ_!12 type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">user —n apc —pw abcXYZ_!12</codeph>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Type <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">quit</codeph> or <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">exit</codeph> to log out.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reset</uicontrol> button
on the front panel to reboot the NMC.</p>
            </li>
